en: The Joint Market Monitoring Initiative (JMMI) is a joint initiative from the Somalia Water, Sanitation and Hygiene (WASH), Shelter, and Education clusters and REACH. It aims to address an information gap in Somalia in terms of regular and updated monitoring of market functionality and a broad range of non-food items (NFIs), while contributing to existing supply chain and price monitoring of the main minimum expenditure basket (MEB) items.
so: Hindisaha wada jirka ah ee koormeerka suuqa (JMMI) waa iskaashi wadajir ah oo ka yimid hay'adaha ka shaqeeya Biyaha, Fayadhowrka iyo Nadaafadda (WASH), Hoyga iyo Waxbarashada ee Somaaliya iyo haayada REACH. Ujeeddadeedu waa inay wax ka qabato farqiga macluumaadka ee ka jira Soomaaliya marka la eego kormeerka joogtada ah ee la cusbooneysiiyey ee ku saabsan shaqada suuqa iyo waxyaabaha aan cuntada ahayn (NFIs), iyadoo gacan ka geysaneysa silsiladda jirta iyo la socodka qiimaha ugu yar (MEB) ee alaabta.

so: Tixraac furaha (kor) sharaxaad ku saabsan sida loo aqriyo jaantuskan (garaafka).Tilmaamaha shayga la qiimeyay ayaa laga heli karaa hoosta.Xaaladaha saamiyada, waxyaabaha leh in ka badan hal qeexitaan ayaa la isku daraa.Jaantuskani waa mid sidaa dooneysid u isticmaali kartid; waad weyneeyn kartaa oo jiirka ayaad ku wareejin kartaa si aad u hesho macluumaad dheeraad ah, iyo qalabka kale ee laga heli karo geeska kore ee midig ee garaafkan.

en: Primary data is collected quarterly through interviews with market vendors purposively selected from the targeted markets. The clusters' partners are responsible for data collection. In this first round, 491 interviews were collected from 12 locations between August 9-12, 2020. As vendors were purposively selected, findings are not statistically representative. To prevent spread and contraction of COVID-19, data was collected remotely. This situation limited the capacity of enumerators to target specific vendors. In addition, it limited possibilities of follow up with vendors. All findings are indicative only, and only apply to the period within which data was collected. Moreover, item specifications may vary slightly between locations according to different brands available, and comparability between the locations assessed is limited.
so: Xogta aasaasiga ah waxaa la uruuriyaa seddexdii biloodba mar iyadoo wareysiyada lala yeesho ganacsatada suuqa iyadoo si ula kac ah loo xushay suuqyada la bartilmaameedsaday. Hay'adaha qeybta ka ah daladan ayaa mas'uul ka ah ururinta xogta.Wareeggan koowaad, 491 wareysi ayaa laga soo uruuriyay 12 goobood inta udhaxeysa bishii sideedaad ilaa bishii labiyo tobnaad ee sanadkan 2020.  Maaddaama iibiyeyaashu si ula kac ah loo xushay, natiijooyinka ma ahan kuwo tirakoob wakiil ah. Si looga hortago faafitaanka iyo qaadida  COVID-19, xogta ayaa lagu uruuriyay hab fog oo wicitaan ah. Xaaladdaani waxay xaddiday awoodda xog uruuriyayaashu inay beegsadaan iibiyayaal gaar ah. Intaas waxaa sii dheer, waxay xadiday fursadaha dib-u-tixraacida iibiyeyaasha. Dhammaan natiijooyinka ayaa ah tilmaamayaal keliya, waxayna khuseeyaan oo keliya muddada lagu soo ururiyay xogta. Intaa waxaa sii dheer, qeexitaannada shayga way kala duwanaan karaan waxoogaa inta udhaxeysa goobaha iyadoo loo eegayo noocyo kala duwan oo la heli karo, iyo isbarbardhiga u dhexeeya goobaha la qiimeeyay wuu xadidan yahay.

en: The WASH and Shelter clusters are responsible for the identification of partners, among cluster members, willing to contribute to the JMMI. The clusters also lead external coordination with the Humanitarian Country Team (HCT) stakeholders and government actors. Cluster members identified as partners provide data collection capacity according to their access and availability, and support the study with sector-specific expertise. REACH is responsible for leading the tools and analysis framework design, training of partners and technical support for data collection, supporting focal points in managing the field data collection, leads on technical data management and data cleaning, data analysis, and output production. The geographic coverage area is determined by the access and capacity of partners. In order to maximize efficacy, certain markets are prioritized to reflect the areas in which cash transfer programs, particularly focused on NFIs, are planned or ongoing, as well as key supply chains for the main NFIs assessed.
so: Dalada (cluster) biyaha iyo fayadhawrka (WASH) iyo Hoyga ayaa mas'uul ka ah soo xulida hay'adaha qeybta ka noqonaya  , xubnaha ka tirsan Dalada ee doonaya inay wax ku biiriyaan JMMI. Dalada ayaa sidoo kale horseed u ah  isuduwidda dibedda ee daneeyayaasha Kooxaha Bani'aadamnimada ee Kooxda (HCT) iyo hawlwadeennada dawladda.Xubnaha Dalada loo aqoonsaday inay ka mid noqdaan ayaa bixiya awoodda xog uruurinta iyadoo loo eegayo marin u helistooda iyo helitaankoodaba, waxayna ku taageeraan daraasadda khibrad gaar u ah. REACH waxay mas'uul ka tahay hogaaminta aaladaha iyo qaabeynta falanqaynta, tababarka hay'adaha qeybta ka ah iyo taageerada farsamo ee xog aruurinta, taageerida uqaabilsanaha xug uruurinta goob waliba, maareynta xog aruurinta, waxay horseed u tahay maareynta xogta farsamada iyo nadiifinta xogta, falanqaynta xogta, iyo soo saarka warbixinada.Goobaha la qiimeeyey waxaa go'aaminaya helitaanka iyo awoodda hay'adaha qeybta ka ah Dalada e ka qeyb qaadanaya xog uruurinta. Si kor loogu qaado waxtarka, suuqyada qaarkood ayaa mudnaanta la siiyaa si ay u muujiyaan meelaha barnaamijyada lacag-bixinta, gaar ahaan diiradda la saarayo walxaha ama shayda aan cuntada ahayn NFI-yada, la qorsheynayo ama socda, iyo sidoo kale silsilado muhiim ah oo loogu talagalay NFI-yada waaweyn ee la qiimeeyay.

en: The logarithmic scale grows exponentially. The figure on the right starts at 0.5 and goes to 20. Only multiples of 10 are written in full, while other numbers (in this case 2 and 5) are guidances. This scale highlights differences in smaller numbers, and minimizes differences around larger numbers.
so: Qiyaasta logarithmic ayaa si aad ah u koraysa.Jaantuska dhanka midig wuxuu ka bilaabanayaa 0.5 wuxuuna aadayaa 20. Kaliya 10 jibaarayaal ayaa si buuxda loo qoraa, halka tirooyinka kale (kiiskan 2 iyo 5) ay yihiin hageyaal.Qiyaastaani waxay muujineysaa kala duwanaanshaha tirada yar, waxayna yareyneysaa kala duwanaanshaha ku saabsan tirooyinka waaweyn.
